1. 订单发货控制器 包裹

1.1. 查询所有未发货商品

URL: /gruul-mall-order/order/{orderNo}/shopOrder/{shopOrderNo}/undelivered

Type: GET

Author: 张治保 date 2022/7/26

Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=UTF-8

Description: 查询所有未发货商品

Query-parameters:

Parameter Type Description Required Since

orderNo

string

订单号

false

-

shopOrderNo

string

店铺订单号

false

-

shopId

int64

店铺id

false

-

sellType

enum

商品销售类型<br/>(See: 销售类型)

false

-

supplierId

int64

供应商id

false

-

Request-example:

curl -X GET -i /gruul-mall-order/order/{orderNo}/shopOrder/{shopOrderNo}/undelivered?shopId=0&sellType=PURCHASE&supplierId=0&orderNo=&shopOrderNo=
